<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <div>
        <h1>Verify Your Email</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>Welcome <%= username %>!</p>

        <p>
          Thank you for signing up! To complete your account setup and start
          using our services, please verify your email address using the code
          below.
        </p>

        <div>
          <div>Your Verification Code</div>
          <div><b><%= verifyOTP %></b></div>
          <div>This code expires in 2 Hours</div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div>Welcome to Our Platform!</div>
          <p>
            Once verified, you'll have access to all our features and services.
            We're excited to have you join our community!
          </p>
        </div>

        <p>
          If you did not create an account with us, please ignore this email or
          contact our support team if you have concerns.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>
          This is an automated verification email. Please do not reply to this
          message.
        </p>
        <p>Need help? Contact our support team for assistance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
